            "txt_align": "start",
            "sub_heading": "",
            "heading": "Can We Talk About the Men? 5 Times Bollywood Actors Wore Sarees and Owned It",
            "text": "<p>It’s 2026. Men are crying on reels, applying eyeliner better than most of us, and yes — some of them are even rocking <a href=\"https://www.indyvogue.com/?srsltid=AfmBOoqX1yQKCFAAzDr4Q5HamNc7COuqsGPqWE21JcgVRSWzuLj7NO5t\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><strong>sarees</strong></span></a> better than your Pinterest inspo board. So let’s drop the gendered drama and give the spotlight where it’s due.</p><p>Because when a man drapes six yards of elegance and doesn’t flinch at a pleat — <em>that’s</em> what we call <strong>main character energy</strong>.</p><p>Here’s a savage list of 5 times men ditched the tux and walked straight into drape domination in the movies.</p>",
